features.text: View more work by Thomas upstairs (click me)

Thomas is a generative artist located north of Copenhagen, Denmark. He enjoys using code and programming as a creative medium, and for the most parts he builds the tools he uses himself. Thomas is particularly interested in exploring dynamic systems and how these might be captured in a static piece, while retaining the sense of movement.
